com.quinsoft.zeidon

Class TaskLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.slf4j.ext.LoggerWrapper
      • com.quinsoft.zeidon.TaskLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ZeidonLogger, org.slf4j.Logger

    public class TaskLogger
extends org.slf4j.ext.LoggerWrapper
implements ZeidonLogger
    A wrapper around slf4j Logger that supports the following: - Messages use String.format() functionality. - Multiple TaskLogger instances can be created for one logger instance. This allows each task to have its own logging level.
    Author:
    DG
